embeds.title: Stat Projection Info Page
embeds.description:
- The Bedwars Stat Projection feature predicts your stats at any given bedwrs star.
- Projected stats uses session stats for accurate forecasting, so a long session is recommended for precise results.
- You can specify a session for projections otherwise it will be dynamically determined.
- The `/prestige` command gives a detailed breakdown of expected stats and dates.
- The `/year 2024` command predicts your stats for the year 2024, giving a quick overview of your future performance in that year.
